author: Paramount Plus
description:
James Jordan rides up Paramount Mountain on the Peak Talk ski lift with Josh Horowitz to talk all things Landman. A many-time collaborator with Taylor Sheridan, James (Dale Bradley) shares stories of working alongside Billy Bob Thornton (Tommy Norris) and Sam Elliott (T.L.) on Season 2 and what makes Dale a fan-favorite character. James and Josh also hear from Ali Larter (Angela Norris) on how Landman successfully blends drama and humor - often showcased in family dinner scenes.

Stream Landman on Paramount+.

Watch Peak Talk with Josh Horowitz on Paramount+ YouTube.
